IF :SolPan == 1 THEN goto 2 end goto 3
:TR = :TCR + (:LOH * -1) goto 1
:TR = 0 goto 1 end
// SolPan is the Name for the Button
// If the Button is activated, the Panels start turning
// If Button is off, Panel turn back to 0 
// :TR is Turret Rotation, :TCR is current Rotation
// :LOH is the Light Offset Horizontal from Solar Panel
// Panels are continously turning towards the sun
// You need at least one SolarPanel with light sensor
